&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 0&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570377</guid><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 13:35:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Ask HN: Is AI helping with personal projects/tools? What's your stack?</title><link>https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570205</link><description>&lt;p&gt;I have a couple of personal app ideas that need simple cloud storage. I was hoping Claude/Codex would be able to help me put something basic together quickly, but I've been underwhelmed by tech stack suggestions they tend to suggest.&lt;p&gt;They either push solutions that don't really fit (claude suggested claude artifacts) or are overkill for a single person app (e.g. "firebase + tauri + sveltekit").&lt;p&gt;Curious what stack people are using for personal projects/tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comments URL: &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570205"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570205&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Points: 1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 0&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570205</guid><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 13:24:39 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Show HN: Mira – Open-source and self-hosted AI code reviewer</title><link>https://github.com/miracodeai/mira</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Hey HN,&lt;p&gt;I'm Jay, co-creator of Mira. An open-source, self-hosted AI code reviewer where you BYOK (bring your own key).&lt;p&gt;Local models are getting really good.&lt;p&gt;Hosted frontier models are getting really expensive.&lt;p&gt;So, we built Mira. Mira has some snazzy features too:&lt;p&gt;- It's really fast at reviewing. Average is 77s compared with Greptile's 5 minutes. Your PRs aren't going into a queue on a cloud somewhere.&lt;p&gt;- Mira performs a blast radius and see what damage will be done with code change.&lt;p&gt;- Learns your codebase's patterns from the repo itself and enforces them without a config file.&lt;p&gt;- It's self-hosted, so your code never leaves your infrastructure. Bring your own model - OpenAI, Anthropic, or a local LLM behind your firewall.&lt;p&gt;We're really active, and looking for active contributors. Come join us in our discord!&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/miracodeai/mira" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://github.com/miracodeai/mira&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thanks,
Jay&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comments URL: &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570197"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48570197&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
